  <article class="mb-8">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ol class="list-disc ml-8">
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="/api/core/activelist/" class="underline high">ActiveList</a>
          now knows whether or not it has been stopped before.
        </p>

        <p>
          A new variable has been added to the
          <a href="/api/core/activelistautoplay/" class="underline high"
            >autoPlay</a
          >
          called
          <a
            href="/api/core/activelistautoplay/#hasBeenStoppedBefore"
            class="underline high"
            >hasBeenStoppedBefore</a
          >. It is a boolean which when `true` means that the `autoPlay` has
          stopped at least once before.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </article>

  <article class="mb-8">
    <h2>Fixes</h2>
    <ol class="list-disc ml-8">
      <li>
        <p>
          The
          <a href="/api/core/activelist/#initialize" class="underline high"
            >initialize</a
          >
          method of the
          <a href="/api/core/activelist/" class="underline high">ActiveList</a>,
          did not reset the
          <a href="/api/core/activelist/#autoPlay" class="underline high"
            >autoPlay</a
          >
          and the
          <a href="/api/core/activelist/#cooldown" class="underline high"
            >cooldown</a
          >
          objects.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
